summary: The mod adds a new armor for the female characters.
descriptionHtml:
The mod adds a new leather armor for the female characters.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Made for bodies CBBE/or CBBE with BBP, But it normal work with UNP. 
And Its working great with UNP with sporty sexy muscle map.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Unfortunately, only a light version.
I apologize for this armor, because she has such defiant appearance.
Just me tired to do the fully closed armor, and made me want a something new.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Armor is represented in 4 Colors
gloves in 2 colors
boots in 2 colors
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
how to play/where to find:
You\'ll find it near the Vaytran near the Honning farm. Where there are signs of roads, in the chest near the bridge.
[URL=http://fastpic.ru/][IMG]http://i53.fastpic.ru/big/2013/0329/94/5c7bbe99106d250e1f561d4b1f1fdd94.jpg[/IMG][/URL]
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Optional files:
The archive has optional esp-file for craft in the forge
Optional meshes for BBP are also present.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
installation (standart)
1. Use the Nexus mod manadger to download and install the entire package.
2. open the archive and copy the folder \"date\" in the game folder \"Skyrim\"
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
thanks:
all who endorsed me.
